      "summary": "The Pennsylvania House of Representatives passed a resolution introduced by Rep. Sheryl Delozier designating June 2026 as Scoliosis Awareness Month in Pennsylvania. The resolution is symbolic and does not create law, allocate funding, or mandate any specific programs. Delozier used the occasion to highlight a constituent's personal experience with scoliosis to underscore the importance of early screening.",
